oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Gibson and NCO Nashville Guitar Festival (2002)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Jorgenson, John; Keaggy, Phil; Mason, Brent (Guitarist); Sutton, Bryan; Bitetti, Ernesto; Barenberg, Russ; Anderson, Muriel; Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (black and red on brown) announcing the Gibson and NCO Nashville Guitar Festival with guitarists Muriel Anderson, Russ Barenberg, Ernesto Bitetti, Pete Huttlinger, John Johns, John Jorgenson, Phil Keaggy, Brent Mason, Richard Smith, Bryan Sutton, and William Yelverton in Nashville, Tennessee from March 28 to April 8. Poster features a metal photoplate of the Gibson and NCO Nashville Guitar Festival 2002 logo.
